msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Sinclair - ZX 81 (EightyOne)"
msgstr "Sinclair — ZX 81 (EightyOne)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "EightyOne is an emulator for the range of home computers made by Sinclair Research (and their clones) in the 1980s."
msgstr "EightyOne — это эмулятор линейки домашних компьютеров, выпущенных Sinclair Research (и их клонов) в 1980-х годах."

